{"id":"a1e6a4ab-45c6-4030-b5e3-63a06dd89c03","title":"1512/09/18","type":"main-list-block","children":[{"id":"2dedf016-c120-411b-80e3-98bb1d1283e3","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"From Rome, September 18th, [1512].","standoffProperties":[{"id":"033d05b6-ff90-4f9d-ab2c-438890029167","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":5,"end":8,"value":"501a8a32-2c8a-4934-9060-8c7e36339f0f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"38f87f6b-ad51-4521-b4d5-73b8090c860e","type":"codex/time-reference","start":11,"end":32,"value":"bb412b7d-40c7-4734-a08c-1a6d7f65fff6","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"fae87e2f-9550-447e-b98e-b05ba3d2d0a3","type":"style/superscript","start":23,"end":24,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"243fe791-6597-4aa3-9b40-896f197d969a","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"To Buonarroto di Lodovico Simoni,","standoffProperties":[{"id":"721d3bda-9691-492c-b0c1-79367ca2a808","type":"style/italics","start":0,"end":31,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"6a50f102-e494-4afb-b8e6-223304ce94b2","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":3,"end":31,"value":"eb5c2755-f869-4ca7-8733-1c39b95bc7a0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"5a60ca12-e808-497f-b4ac-52cc17ed6a59","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"in Florence.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"4660af5c-6a0d-49f1-99b8-a1fd6dd352a6","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":3,"end":10,"value":"671ee7e7-ae1b-4a5a-9591-b40203d5108f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"8200b654-13a8-4370-a528-63c5e66b4763","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"BUONARROTO,\u00A0\u2014\u00A0I read in thy last letter about the great peril which was menacing the Territory, and I was exceedingly distressed at the news. It is now said that the Medici have returned to Florence\u00A0and that everything has quieted down. I suppose, therefore, that the threatened danger\u00A0\u2014\u00A0from the Spaniards, that to say\u00A0\u2014\u00A0is averted, and that there is now no need for ye to flee from the city. Remain\u00A0peacefully where ye are, therefore, and be neither friendly nor confidential with anybody, save with God\u00A0alone; neither speak about anybody, whether it be\u00A0good or ill, for the end of this business is still obscure. Let your own affairs occupy all your thoughts.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"d53432e5-b52d-4114-b7d4-3d1b17da2f97","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":0,"end":9,"value":"eb5c2755-f869-4ca7-8733-1c39b95bc7a0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"a629532f-8879-459a-adad-0fa2d890f251","type":"codex/claim-reference","start":14,"end":140,"value":"eba99a2d-44d4-4a27-8527-8809daae3cde","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"8cada62a-5109-4c7e-be0a-da59dc3c2dfb","type":"highlight","start":14,"end":139,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"2f3109ad-f087-48ca-8ef5-e795b3d337dd","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":14,"end":14,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"dd871ddf-6077-4052-91b5-2f1081677923","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":24,"end":26,"value":"eb5c2755-f869-4ca7-8733-1c39b95bc7a0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"77175ab4-a9f8-4b54-aa93-c2a8d5a7c97e","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":100,"end":100,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"a766981c-2471-40ef-884f-db79dbb50ed7","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":166,"end":171,"value":"f58ed5e3-a380-4e53-aa74-f7a8e7e7b3eb","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"61089531-1313-4833-a07a-4d20c4f13c40","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":190,"end":197,"value":"671ee7e7-ae1b-4a5a-9591-b40203d5108f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"382973e0-8bef-4e5f-bfea-ada6eb8a7293","type":"codex/document-reference","start":198,"end":198,"value":"6784ba06-be98-4ffe-ba92-35405bfb49a6","zeroPoint":true,"metadata":[]},{"id":"1015467b-c845-4987-9b79-5266b051844e","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":237,"end":237,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"fe81cfc2-4558-48ec-a45a-a419fdee9270","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":368,"end":369,"value":"eb5c2755-f869-4ca7-8733-1c39b95bc7a0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"1030b46d-7296-4d97-ba92-9943cea82d7f","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":418,"end":419,"value":"eb5c2755-f869-4ca7-8733-1c39b95bc7a0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"b2deda8c-6909-44a4-bed8-174b4c09997a","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":502,"end":504,"value":"a3fed3ec-1814-4027-a2d5-ac598b2fcb6f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"23239418-053d-4569-bb0b-ad555c758871","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":620,"end":623,"value":"eb5c2755-f869-4ca7-8733-1c39b95bc7a0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"13dab212-db09-49fd-9b74-37648e012370","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":648,"end":651,"value":"eb5c2755-f869-4ca7-8733-1c39b95bc7a0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"63eb985e-b7f5-41ea-b22e-412f4c2a454b","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"As to the forty ducats Lodovico withdrew from\u00A0Santa Maria Nuova, I wrote a letter the other day\u00A0to say that if ye should be in danger for your lives\u00A0he was to draw not forty ducats but all I have. I did not, however, give him permission to take the money for any other purpose. I must tell you that\u00A0I have not a single grosso, and I could almost say of\u00A0myself that I go barefoot and naked: and I shall only receive the remainder of my money when I\u00A0have finished this work. Meanwhile I suffer the\u00A0greatest inconvenience and hardships. Therefore, if ye likewise should have to bear with some discomfort do not be impatient, and as long as ye have money of your own do not take mine, except in times\u00A0of peril, as I have already said. However, if ye\u00A0should be in dire necessity from any cause, I beg of\u00A0you to write first to me, if it so please you. I shall\u00A0return to you soon. If it please God, I shall certainly\u00A0not fail to be with you for the feast of All Saints.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"17d31a87-c9fc-410b-a56b-aa6f7d802809","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":23,"end":30,"value":"21671569-3eea-412b-85cc-08f659f58019","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"0430d3a1-f7ef-4da4-b640-a4c805cfb31c","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":46,"end":62,"value":"73ddae0b-7cdf-4c62-a3de-69f9219d9fe5","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"ea648006-7e24-4165-ae6f-f013ddb7aaea","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":65,"end":65,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"7cf137ed-cc53-4e7c-9658-4ad83e532caa","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":111,"end":112,"value":"eb5c2755-f869-4ca7-8733-1c39b95bc7a0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"8cfb43dc-14e3-44f7-813d-32d4aad4fb0c","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":138,"end":141,"value":"eb5c2755-f869-4ca7-8733-1c39b95bc7a0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"50e2c7b8-317c-4584-931d-489274d41df1","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":149,"end":150,"value":"21671569-3eea-412b-85cc-08f659f58019","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"c876a11f-89ad-469f-ad33-381de0eab6e3","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":189,"end":189,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"e5663b03-6d68-43bd-8f69-c8c54ce44035","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":197,"end":197,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"c0c4ff90-2c22-43fe-a28f-6a37093235ee","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":222,"end":224,"value":"21671569-3eea-412b-85cc-08f659f58019","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"874366a2-4135-4716-998f-714cccc32332","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":278,"end":278,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"32200d09-252c-440d-89cb-b9ff246f6eed","type":